Text::Format

* Numbered paragraphs.
* Numbered lines (including by step).
* Margin lines. e.g.:
     | This is line one.
     | This is line two.
* Block indent/unindent.
* Word-breaking:
  * Hard breaking (just continue on next line)
  * Soft breaking (use a marker and continue on next line)
  * Hyphenation (using a hyphenation module)